WEBVTT

00:08:31.390 --> 00:08:33.016
"Pengetua berkata,

00:08:33.016 --> 00:08:38.743
"Saya tidak melatih mereka.
Kami tinggalkan mereka di atas atap.

00:08:39.353 --> 00:08:40.972
Seperti berbiri."

00:08:40.972 --> 00:08:42.401
(Ketawa)

00:08:42.401 --> 00:08:44.230
Mereka tak berhenti berlari.

00:08:44.230 --> 00:08:46.259
(Ketawa)

00:08:46.779 --> 00:08:51.348
Saranan saya, jangan mengawal mereka,

00:08:51.838 --> 00:08:55.060
jangan terlampau melindungi mereka,

00:08:55.060 --> 00:08:58.687
dan ada kalanya mereka tersembam.

00:08:58.687 --> 00:09:01.633
Mereka perlukan sedikit kecederaan.